        <p class="note" MadCap:autonum="&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #bed230;&quot; class=&quot;mcFormatColor&quot;&gt;Note: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;">If you enter text that is too long to fit inside the object and <span class="Emphasis">Auto-size to fit text</span> is disabled, you will see a red plus <img src="../../../Images/Shared/red_plus_btn.png" class="ReduceButtonSize" /> where the text is cut off. This lets you know that you need to manually resize the shape to fit the text. Click the plus to see the text in its entirety. <MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Snippets.Snippet2,General.OnlineOnly,Products.Capture">See <MadCap:xref href="../../../../Capture/Appearance/Setting_the_Rectangle_Properties_for_an_Object.htm" MadCap:conditions="Products.Capture">Setting the Rectangle Properties for an Object</MadCap:xref>.</MadCap:conditionalText><MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Snippets.Snippet2,General.OnlineOnly,Products.Mimic">See <MadCap:xref href="../../../../Mimic/Appearance/Setting-Rectangle-Properties-for-an-Object-Mimic.htm" MadCap:conditions="Products.Mimic">Setting the Rectangle Properties for an Object</MadCap:xref>.</MadCap:conditionalText></p>
